This plugin's module shape, mock-client test pattern, and replay
orchestrator semantics borrow heavily from:

  Smart-Coders-HQ/opencode-model-fallback (Apache-2.0)
  https://github.com/Smart-Coders-HQ/opencode-model-fallback

Net-new contributions on top of that reference:
  - TTFT (time-to-first-token) timer layer
  - Integration with the omr Go authoring TUI via the shared
    schema/fallback-schema.json contract
  - Canonical config path `agent.<name>.options.fallback_models`
    aligned with OpenCode's documented `AgentConfig.normalize()` slot
